Removed the "Date Edited" column from the preview table on the upload contacts page. Changes:

1. Removed the "Date Edited" header from the table (line 268)
2. Removed the "Date Edited" data cell from the table body (line 281)

The column no longer appears in the preview table when a CSV is uploaded. The data is still parsed and saved to the database, but it's not shown in the preview.

No linting errors. The table now shows: First Name, Last Name, Email, Phone Number, LinkedIn Profile, Date added, and Source.
